{"tid":1877754,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"姜丹尼爾被選為“情人節最想送巧克力的男愛豆”一位！","createTime":"2020-02-13T07:58:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-13T13:47:33.000Z","uid":74065,"like":2,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"bdd4d3981895be382bcdd1a17885583d45b566c2","tid":1877754,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T07:58:14.000Z","msg":"姜丹尼爾被選為&ldquo;情人節最想送巧克力的男愛豆&rdquo;一位！<br />\n<br />\n在&ldquo;情人節最想送巧克力的男愛豆&rdquo;投票中，姜丹尼爾獲得了一位。 IDOL人氣排名服務平台&ldquo;最愛偶像&rdquo;在2月6日~12日一周的時間裡選擇9名偶像候選人以&ldquo;情人節想送巧克力的男愛豆&rdquo;為主題發起了投票活動，結果顯示參與投票的32,768名中有9,679名選擇了姜丹尼爾。另外，姜丹尼爾出演的旅行真人秀節目《你好，丹尼爾》將於3月通過SBS FiL播出<br />\n<br />\n投到佢第一 係咪當佢條女透明<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06e94cb85be498a0fcdc88b8f12d7be817bc4a22","tid":1877754,"uid":34071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T08:05:58.000Z","msg":"山婆已經係粒朱古力啦<br />\n拉"},{"pid":"61586fb1eef5de2bfa7a6e05b3278f9942740ccf","tid":1877754,"uid":89931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T08:45:22.000Z","msg":"buddy又酸？"},{"pid":"bcf7e07326784ae8bcc57744dc263096c687acfd","tid":1877754,"uid":231908,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T09:02:58.000Z","msg":"人地鐘意飲奶"},{"pid":"fac25e65f151bb93d04790b8e1545ea74ec15f9f","tid":1877754,"uid":74065,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"61586fb1eef5de2bfa7a6e05b3278f9942740ccf","tid":1877754,"uid":89931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T08:45:22.000Z","msg":"buddy又酸？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T09:25:14.000Z","msg":"TWICE條仔酸乜9..."},{"pid":"02dc52b530c5ff5b8621eb4bad96f1f205c633b4","tid":1877754,"uid":137569,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"06e94cb85be498a0fcdc88b8f12d7be817bc4a22","tid":1877754,"uid":34071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":